              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "Founded in 2009, Omphile Botshelo Construction has grown from a small local builder into one of South Africa's most trusted construction partners. We bring integrity and craftsmanship to every project we undertake.",
