              "fill": "#4A4E54",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "Our team of skilled professionals has delivered infrastructure across residential, commercial, and government sectors. From foundations to finishes, we oversee every detail with care.",
